Class GroupByGroupingComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparator
      • csc555.ebratt.depaul.edu.GroupByGroupingComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator, org.apache.hadoop.io.RawComparator

    public class GroupByGroupingComparator
extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparator
    GroupByGroupingComparator is a custom comparator used in a hadoop job to ensure that GroupByCountPair objects are grouped using their groupBy fields.
